         reading from the dropdown menu. 
         Choose between "Normal," "ST-T Wave Abnormality," or "Left Ventricular Hypertrophy."
  </p>
     <h2> ST Slope</h2>
      <p>Choose the slope of the ST segment during peak exercise. Select either "Flat" or "Up Slopping" from the dropdown menu.
